Package: apathe
Title: American Psychological Association Thesis with R Markdown
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Frederik", "Aust", email = "frederik.aust@uni-koeln.de", role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-4900-788X"))
Description: Provides R Markdown document formats for theses that conform to American Psychological Association manuscript guidelines.
URL: https://github.com/crsh/apathe
BugReports: https://github.com/crsh/apathe/issues
Imports:
    papaja (>= 0.1.2)
SystemRequirements: Rendering the document template requires
  pandoc (>= 2.0; https://pandoc.org) and for PDFs a TeX distribution,
  such as TinyTeX (>= 0.12; https://yihui.org/tinytex/)
